import React from 'react'
import { Button, Typography } from '@material-ui/core'
import { TabButtonsContainer } from '../../styles'

const UserPageInfo = () => {
    return (
        <>  
            <TabButtonsContainer>
                <Button color="primary" variant="outlined">Calculating and Understanding Caloric Needs</Button>
                <Button color="primary" variant="outlined">Calorie Intake Calculation</Button>
                <Button color="primary" variant="outlined">Interpreting the results</Button>
            </TabButtonsContainer>
            
            <InfoTabsDiv>

            </InfoTabsDiv>
            
        </>
    )
}

export default UserPageInfo
